_runtime.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n- `BuildRuntime` class with methods:\n  - `build(workspace_path, **options)` - main orchestration\n  - `_increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)` - semver patch bump, None->0.0.1, fallback `{version}-1`\n  - `_validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path, metadata)` - checks metadata, Dockerfile, Docker availability\n  - `_build_local(workspace_path, metadata, options)` - Docker build with optional proxy\n  - `_build_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)` - placeholder cloud build\n  - `_update_build_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, build_result, tag)` - updates metadata.image\n\n#### 4.5 agentcube/services/docker_service.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n- `DockerService` class with methods:\n  - `check_docker_available()` - uses `docker.from_env()` + `client.ping()`\n  - `build_image(dockerfile_path, context_path, image_name, tag, build_args)` - returns dict with image_name, image_id, image_size, build_time\n  - `_format_size(size_bytes)` - formats B/KB/MB/GB\n\n#### 4.6 agentcube/services/metadata_service.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n- `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model with validators for language, build_mode, port\n- `MetadataService` class: `load_metadata`, `save_metadata`, `update_metadata`, `validate_workspace`\n- Fallback chain: `agent_metadata.yaml` -> `agent.yaml` -> `metadata.yaml`\n\n#### 4.7 agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n- `PackRuntime` class with full pack implementation (workspace validation, metadata, Do